<p>Jet Dental on-site providing dental cleanings and professional teeth whitening </p>

<p>Group fitness sessions including Zumba and Pilates </p>

<p>Healthy cooking demonstrations </p>

<p>Body composition analysis </p>

<p>Giveaways and prizes </p>

<p>Music, food, and more</p>

